@startuml
[*] --> Ready
Ready --> StartMonitoring : Activate
Ready --> Stop : TurnOff
Ready --> Stop : Deactivate
StartMonitoring --> AlarmAndAlerts : SensorTriggered
AlarmAndAlerts --> ContinueMonitoring : FalseAlarmOrTimeEnded
ContinueMonitoring --> Stop : UserEnterPassword
Stop --> Ready : Reset
@enduml
